cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CR 

The paper focuses on using deep learning algorithms for object detection in UAV images of wildlife, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses techniques for improving the accuracy of the model, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the use of UAVs for wildlife monitoring is a topic in robotics (cs.RO) and the paper discusses the challenges of processing large datasets, which is related to computer networks and communications (cs.CR).
